{
  "id": "harmonic_oscillation",
  "subject": "university_physics_1",
  "title_en": "Harmonic Oscillations (University)",
  "title_he": "„™„†„Х„У„Х„™ „Ф„®„Ю„Х„†„Щ„Х„™ („Р„Х„†„Щ„С„®„°„Щ„Ш„Ф)",
  "duration_min": 24,
  "type": "interactive",
  "level_min": "university",
  "agent_hints": "SHM is defined by $a=-\\omega^2 x$, not merely 'sinusoidal looking'. Students confuse $\\omega$ (rad/s) with $f$ (Hz) and $T$. For energy, $E=\\frac{1}{2}kA^2$ is constant; at general $x$, $KE+PE=kA^2/2$. Small-angle pendulum requires $\\theta\\lesssim 15¬∞$.",
  "sections": [
    {
      "id": "shm_definition",
      "title_en": "Simple Harmonic Motion вАФ Definition and Solution",
      "title_he": "„™„†„Х„Ґ„Ф „Ф„®„Ю„Х„†„Щ„™ „§„©„Х„Ш„Ф вАФ „Ф„Т„У„®„Ф „Х„§„™„®„Х„Я",
      "body_en_md": "**Definition:** motion with acceleration proportional and opposite to displacement:\n$$\\boxed{a = -\\omega^2 x}$$\n\nGeneral solution:\n$$\\boxed{x(t) = A\\cos(\\omega t + \\phi)}$$\n\n$A$ = amplitude, $\\omega$ = angular frequency (rad/s), $\\phi$ = phase constant (fixed by initial $x_0$, $v_0$).\n\nPeriod: $T = 2\\pi/\\omega$. Frequency: $f = 1/T = \\omega/(2\\pi)$.",
      "body_he_md": "**„Ф„Т„У„®„Ф:** „™„Р„Х„¶„Ф „§„®„Х„§„Х„®„¶„Щ„Х„†„Щ„™ „Х„†„Т„У„Щ„™ „Ь„Ф„Ґ„™„І:\n$$\\boxed{a = -\\omega^2 x}$$\n\n„§„™„®„Х„Я „Ы„Ь„Ь„Щ:\n$$\\boxed{x(t) = A\\cos(\\omega t + \\phi)}$$\n\n$A$ = „Юplitud„Ф, $\\omega$ = „™„У„Щ„®„Х„™ „Ц„Х„Х„Щ„™„Щ„™, $\\phi$ = „І„С„Х„Ґ „§–∞–Ј„Ф.\n\n„Ц„Ю„Я „Ю„Ч„Ц„Х„®: $T = 2\\pi/\\omega$.",
      "level_min": "university"
    },
    {
      "id": "shm_kinematics",
      "title_en": "Velocity and Acceleration in SHM",
      "title_he": "„Ю„Ф„Щ„®„Х„™ „Х„™„Р„Х„¶„Ф „С-SHM",
      "body_en_md": "Differentiate $x(t) = A\\cos(\\omega t + \\phi)$:\n\n$$v(t) = \\frac{dx}{dt} = -A\\omega\\sin(\\omega t + \\phi)$$\n\n$$a(t) = \\frac{dv}{dt} = -A\\omega^2\\cos(\\omega t + \\phi) = -\\omega^2 x(t)$$\n\n**Key relations:**\n- $|v|_{max} = A\\omega$ at $x=0$.\n- $|a|_{max} = A\\omega^2$ at $|x|=A$.\n- $v$ leads $x$ by $90¬∞$; $a$ is antiparallel to $x$.",
      "body_he_md": "„Т„Ц„Щ„®„Ф „©„Ь $x(t) = A\\cos(\\omega t + \\phi)$:\n\n$$v = -A\\omega\\sin(\\omega t + \\phi), \\quad a = -A\\omega^2\\cos(\\omega t + \\phi) = -\\omega^2 x$$\n\n$|v|_{max} = A\\omega$ „С-$x=0$; $|a|_{max} = A\\omega^2$ „С-$|x|=A$.",
      "level_min": "university"
    },
    {
      "id": "spring_mass",
      "title_en": "SpringвАУMass System",
      "title_he": "„Ю„Ґ„®„Ы„™ „І„§„Щ„•вАУ„Ю„°„Ф",
      "body_en_md": "Hooke's law: $F = -kx$ gives $m\\ddot{x} = -kx$, so:\n$$\\boxed{\\omega = \\sqrt{\\frac{k}{m}}, \\qquad T = 2\\pi\\sqrt{\\frac{m}{k}}}$$\n\nIndependent of amplitude $A$ (ideal spring, no damping).\n\nMultiple springs / masses: reduce to equivalent $k_{eq}$, $m_{eq}$.",
      "body_he_md": "„Ч„Х„І „Ф„Х„І: $F = -kx$ „†„Х„™„Я $m\\ddot{x} = -kx$:\n$$\\boxed{\\omega = \\sqrt{k/m}, \\quad T = 2\\pi\\sqrt{m/k}}$$\n\n„Ь„Р „™„Ь„Х„Щ „С-$A$ („І„§„Щ„• „Р„Щ„У„Щ„Р„Ь„Щ, „Ь„Ь„Р „®„Щ„°„Х„Я).",
      "level_min": "university"
    },
    {
      "id": "simple_pendulum",
      "title_en": "Simple Pendulum вАФ Small Angles",
      "title_he": "„Ю„Ш„Х„Ш„Ь„™ „§„©„Х„Ш„Ф вАФ „Ц„Х„Х„Щ„Х„™ „І„Ш„†„Х„™",
      "body_en_md": "For string length $L$ and small angle $\\theta$ (in radians, $\\theta \\lesssim 15¬∞$):\n$$\\sin\\theta \\approx \\theta \\quad \\Rightarrow \\quad \\ddot{\\theta} = -\\frac{g}{L}\\theta$$\n\n$$\\boxed{\\omega = \\sqrt{\\frac{g}{L}}, \\qquad T = 2\\pi\\sqrt{\\frac{L}{g}}}$$\n\nValid only for small oscillations; large angles increase period.",
      "body_he_md": "„Ь„Ю„Х„Ш „Р„Х„®„Ъ $L$ „Х„Ц„Х„Х„Щ„™ „І„Ш„†„Ф $\\theta$ („®„У„Щ„Р„†„Щ„Э, $\\theta \\lesssim 15¬∞$):\n$$\\omega = \\sqrt{g/L}, \\quad T = 2\\pi\\sqrt{L/g}$$\n\n„™„І„£ „®„І „Ь„™„†„Х„У„Х„™ „І„Ш„†„Х„™.",
      "level_min": "university"
    },
    {
      "id": "shm_energy",
      "title_en": "Energy in SHM",
      "title_he": "„Р„†„®„Т„Щ„Ф „С-SHM",
      "body_en_md": "Total mechanical energy (no damping):\n$$\\boxed{E = \\frac{1}{2}kA^2 = \\frac{1}{2}m v_{max}^2}$$\n\nAt displacement $x$:\n$$KE = \\frac{1}{2}k(A^2 - x^2), \\qquad PE = \\frac{1}{2}kx^2$$\n\nEnergy oscillates between kinetic and potential; $E$ is constant.",
      "body_he_md": "„Р„†„®„Т„Щ„Ф „Ю„Ы„†„Щ„™ „Ы„Х„Ь„Ь„™:\n$$E = \\frac{1}{2}kA^2 = \\frac{1}{2}mv_{max}^2$$\n\n„С„Ф„Ґ„™„І $x$: $KE = \\frac{1}{2}k(A^2-x^2)$, $PE = \\frac{1}{2}kx^2$.",
      "level_min": "university"
    },
    {
      "id": "damped_oscillations",
      "title_en": "Damped Oscillations вАФ Overview",
      "title_he": "„™„†„Х„У„Х„™ „Ю„®„Х„°„†„Х„™ вАФ „°„І„Щ„®„Ф",
      "body_en_md": "Linear damping: $F_{damp} = -b\\dot{x}$ gives:\n$$m\\ddot{x} + b\\dot{x} + kx = 0$$\n\nDefine $\\gamma = b/(2m)$, $\\omega_0 = \\sqrt{k/m}$.\n\n**Underdamped** ($\\gamma < \\omega_0$):\n$$x(t) = Ae^{-\\gamma t}\\cos(\\omega' t + \\phi), \\quad \\omega' = \\sqrt{\\omega_0^2 - \\gamma^2}$$\n\n**Critical:** $\\gamma = \\omega_0$ (fastest return without oscillation).\n**Overdamped:** $\\gamma > \\omega_0$ (exponential decay, no oscillation).\n\nQuality factor: $Q \\approx \\omega_0/(2\\gamma)$ (energy decay per cycle).",
      "body_he_md": "„®„Щ„°„Х„Я „Ь„Щ„†„Р„®„Щ: $F_{damp} = -b\\dot{x}$:\n$$m\\ddot{x} + b\\dot{x} + kx = 0$$\n\n**„™„Ч„™-„®„Щ„°„Х„Я** ($\\gamma < \\omega_0$): $x = Ae^{-\\gamma t}\\cos(\\omega' t + \\phi)$.\n**„І„®„Щ„Ш„Щ:** $\\gamma = \\omega_0$. **„Щ„™„®-„®„Щ„°„Х„Я:** $\\gamma > \\omega_0$.",
      "level_min": "university"
    },
    {
      "id": "physical_pendulum",
      "title_en": "Physical Pendulum",
      "title_he": "„Ю„Ш„Х„Ш„Ь„™ „§„Щ„Ц„Щ„І„Ь„Щ„™",
      "body_en_md": "Rigid body pivoting about fixed point: torque about pivot $\\tau = -MgL_{cm}\\sin\\theta \\approx -MgL_{cm}\\theta$ for small $\\theta$.\n\n$$\\boxed{\\omega = \\sqrt{\\frac{MgL_{cm}}{I_{pivot}}}, \\qquad T = 2\\pi\\sqrt{\\frac{I_{pivot}}{MgL_{cm}}}}$$\n\n$L_{cm}$ = distance from pivot to center of mass; $I_{pivot}$ about pivot axis.",
      "body_he_md": "„Т„Х„£ „І„©„Щ„Ч „°„С„Щ„С „†„І„Х„У„Ф „І„С„Х„Ґ„Ф:\n$$\\omega = \\sqrt{MgL_{cm}/I_{pivot}}, \\quad T = 2\\pi\\sqrt{I_{pivot}/(MgL_{cm})}$$\n\n$L_{cm}$ = „Ю„®„Ч„І „Ю„¶„Щ„® „Ь„Ю„®„Ы„Ц „Ю„°„Ф; $I_{pivot}$ „°„С„Щ„С „Ф„¶„Щ„®.",
      "level_min": "university"
    }
  ],
